{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440500/extras/November-Trailer-2023__online-video-cutter.com_.gif?t=1710531247\" /><br><br>Start on an epic adventure of square proportions! Explore mysterious zones, conquer challenging puzzles, and engage in thrilling battles with fierce foes.<br>Unlock the full potential of your hero by collecting powerful items scattered throughout the land. The greatest of adventurers will discover hidden treasures waiting for only the bravest of explorers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440500/extras/November-Trailer-2023__online-video-cutter.com___1___2_.gif?t=1710531247\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440500/extras/about-gameplay-heading.png?t=1710531247\" /><br><br><strong>Parry bullets!</strong><br>Once discovered, the <i>Parry Bullet</i> power allows you to parry incoming bullets and reflect them back at enemies!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440500/extras/hsq-parry-explainer-ezgif.com-optimize__9_.gif?t=1710531247\" /><br><br><strong>Explore for secrets!</strong><br>Does it look like a good fit? In HeroSquare secrets are everywhere, and good positioning is the key to many of them!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440500/extras/hsq-secrets-explainer-ezgif.com-resize__1_.gif?t=1710531247\" /><br><br><strong>Power up!</strong><br>On your adventure you will add new abilities and upgrades to your arsenal. Master them to reach the finale of HeroSquare!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440500/extras/pu-hsq.gif?t=1710531247\" /><br><br><strong>Triumph in battle!</strong><br>You will face tough bosses determined 